All desks, chairs, bins, shelves, the skeleton, and plants now rest cleanly on the floor. Walls have been raised by 0.05 m, the blackboard faces the students, the teacher’s chair sits behind its desk, the tall bookshelf is shifted off the wall, and the curtains are pulled into the room.
